Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.68,0:22:18.27,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}若要喚出情感之名 則無休無止無窮無盡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.31,0:22:26.36,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}你的眼神傳來呼喚 我以本能即可分辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.36,0:22:28.20,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}相伴相隨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.45,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}不離不棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:33.03,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無論光明抑或黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.03,0:22:36.91,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}如緊湊相連的拼圖零片
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.91,0:22:41.17,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}一切皆有其因果
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.58,0:22:45.42,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}萍水相逢也好 命中注定也罷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.42,0:22:50.09,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}終將指引我們走向所堅信的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.14,0:22:56.85,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}赤誠真心 逐步升温
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.85,0:23:00.69,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}無虛情假意 非利益所趨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.69,0:23:05.44,KHJ_ED_CN,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\be4\shad5}以真實自我
